	- 4 Bit Revision Number
	- (Status & 0xF000) >> 12

Bits 11-8; Mask 0x0F00
	- 4 Bit Build Number
	- (Status & 0x0F00) >> 8

Bit 3: Mask 0b11100
	GPS Indicator
	First Bit (0b10000): Type
		1: Geolocation
		0: GPS
	Last 2 Bits (0b01100): Quality
		11: Best
		      â€¦
